{"tid":1840693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廣東省都識發sms叫大家注意防疫，港共只識發sms叫大家唔好示威","createTime":"2020-01-25T03:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T03:28:45.000Z","uid":48040,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4f37b2f9de06d230d4119d449b6198da3828fa","tid":1840693,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHnZ1Y9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHnZ1Y9.png&h=885412e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgXZ1Zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgXZ1Zk.png&h=fc66e4d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c22c9ef0f62d2ecc925ea4b8780a8ec67b86c4b5","tid":1840693,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=f119b11e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n但係件事未完！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要繼續話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f2f01a678932908cfe0d00d7f02b9e2b1df360dc","tid":1840693,"uid":239353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"唔需要執著班垃圾高官會做咩<br />\n反正sms都係廢 冇實質行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188cc1c705df250e17f645f6826c6975cd908563","tid":1840693,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"廣東不嬲都高質 支持廣獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fd74475481676907383ac47d969fd74d73abef","tid":1840693,"uid":145736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff4f37b2f9de06d230d4119d449b6198da3828fa","tid":1840693,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHnZ1Y9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHnZ1Y9.png&h=885412e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgXZ1Zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgXZ1Zk.png&h=fc66e4d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:12:08.000Z","msg":"你點收到的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9304debde1011f61bc24ad93e596de86debbd77","tid":1840693,"uid":251292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"你點收的"},{"pid":"100328fb199d34f5a27dae31e6214e4d42e0bd5f","tid":1840693,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:12:22.000Z","msg":"香港垃圾到。叫人唔病唔使戴口罩。戇鳩"},{